    "§A3 provides a detailed analysis.Given our goals, it is natural to ask whether audit trails produced by Pd-Ros alone do not suffice to protect citizen privacy.",
    "The regulatory authority could itself periodically query all delivery drones in operation, check the audit trails to determine whether the drones are in compliance, and publish a compliance report for all drones on a public forum for all citizens to see.",
